Class VarDef

java.lang.Object
  org.mcm.sws.annotation.VarDef
All Implemented Interfaces:
URIIdentifiable
public class VarDef
extends java.lang.Object
implements URIIdentifiable

This class represents the "op-def/input/var" and "op-def/output/var" elements in SESMA descriptions (c.f. http://elektra.mcm.unisg.ch/pbwsc/docs/sd_ecows.pdf )

Author:
Joachim Peer
